n graphs, posets of width at\nmost two and the corresponding bichains. We characterize hereditary classes of\nfinite bipartite permutation graphs which remain wqo when labels from a wqo are\nadded.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Dec 2021 17:29:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 20:57:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-30"}
