ay be of\ninterest to governments and healthcare authorities for devising effective\nvaccination and treatment campaigns during an epidemic outbreak.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 06:47:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
