led a fine\nstructure in the Moscow component. Using the analysis of centralities, a group\nof main characters has been detected. The central characters of the novel are\nKoroviev, Margarita, Bezdomny, Woland, Behemoth, Azazello, Bosoi, Warenukha,\nMaster, and Levi Matthew.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 07:16:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 03:38:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 11:04:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2023 08:56:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
