ons at short\nwavelengths, the success of this integration strategy unlocks a broad range of\nnew integrated photonics applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 10:47:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Dec 2021 01:35:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-13"}
