4)% and (1.9 $\\pm$ 0.1)% were found. A new\nwavelength shifter developed in Italy in collaboration with the Universita\ndegli Studi di Milano-Bicocca will be presented. It allowed to increase the\nlight detection efficiency of about 50% and resulted in an overall efficiency\nof (2.9 $\\pm$ 0.1)% of the X-ARAPUCA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 12:26:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
