 proposed method by using a GOCE satellite 15-day\ncontinuous orbit data. Compared with legacy \"correction - prediction\" method in\nwhich only GOCE data is employed, the accuracy of the 24-hour orbit prediction\nis improved by about 171m the highest for the proposed method. 14-day averaged\n24-hour prediction precision is elevated by approximately 70m.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 15:28:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
